-- Features:
--  - Safe bindable invoke/fire (vararg-safe)
--  - Forward-declared ThinkAsync to avoid nil-call
--  - Single-thinking reuse (no duplicate AI frames)
--  - Automatic size handling for TextLabel + CanvasSize updates
--  - Staged statuses (Thinking (Xs), Searching URL..., etc.)
--  - Error mapping for HTTP and LighterCyan-specific codes
--  - Rate-limiting (50 messages/min) and message-length checks
--  - /fetch <url> handling with fetch stages
